{"tid":965862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大埔老翁過路　遭重型車輾爆頭身亡","createTime":"2019-01-02T11:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-02T14:00:32.000Z","uid":41404,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"704e3ed97ac4588733d030c74c1cc1ef76ad8754","tid":965862,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:10:22.000Z","msg":"大埔發生奪命交通意外，今日(2日)下午5時許，一輛重型勾斗車沿運頭街往南運路方向行駛，至大明里對開時，一名手持拐杖的老翁從行人路步出，重型車疑收掣不及，撞倒老翁後將他捲入車底，老翁頭部被車輪輾過，當場重創昏迷。有途人見狀慌忙喝止司機，同時報警求助。救護員接報趕至，經檢查後證實老翁已傷重死亡。<br />\n<br />\n事後現場遺下一支屬於老翁的拐杖及衣物，有街坊聞訊到場上香拜祭。據悉，死者居於現場附近一間護老院，警方正調查意外原因，重型車司機被帶上警車助查。受意外影響，運頭街介乎鄉事會街與廣福道之間全線封閉，交通十分擠塞。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190102/bkn-20190102175356667-0102_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190102%2Fbkn-20190102175356667-0102_00822_001.html&d=mQHFsxKfgzE2mw2WxC2sDzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=916c9003\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190102/bkn-20190102175356667-0102_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4ac289a1767cf95dbddefbd6710239903b2208c3","tid":965862,"uid":222907,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:11:09.000Z","msg":"講還講"},{"pid":"7254163efaf4159749bdf2389c0340c151af803a","tid":965862,"uid":55924,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:12:14.000Z","msg":"RIP司機"},{"pid":"de0f1c072618ad1a242e5ed86d903e223ed787b8","tid":965862,"uid":71133,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:14:53.000Z","msg":"香港d保險公司應該賣車死廢老保險，實好受歡迎"},{"pid":"041384c3bcc3ca4ce53f809f05327ee6ec11f028","tid":965862,"uid":26451,"like":8,"dislike":5,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:15:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cd1e8680bf8fcc0d8bea60721d762494f11a037f","tid":965862,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T11:15:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\